title: Ay, Don't I Got Zeits? 4/12: Stallone, Ted Nugent, Minnesota,  Macaulay Culkin x Brenda Song, NBA, Hideki Matsuyama, Kid Cudi
itunes:title: Ay, Don't I Got Zeits? 4/12: Stallone, Ted Nugent, Minnesota,  Macaulay Culkin x Brenda Song, NBA, Hideki Matsuyama, Kid Cudi
description:
On this edition of Ay, Don't I Got Zeits? Jack and Miles discuss Stallone joining Mar-a-Lago, and not joining Creed III cast, Ted Nugent's Facebook Live video, the latest Minnesota Police shooting, Macaulay Culkin/Brenda Song's first child, NBA news, Hideki Matsuyama winning the Masters, and Kid Cudi's SNL performance.
